name: Turkey Club Skewer
author: Dietz & Watson
summary: These Turkey Club Skewers are easy to customize and perfect for picnics or on-the-go meals.
ingredients: 4 slices Dietz & Watson Gourmet Smoked Bacon
6 slices Dietz & Watson Originals Herbed Turkey
4 slices Dietz & Watson Originals Cheddar Cheese
directions: Cook Bacon in a cold pan on low until crisp
While bacon is cooking, cut bread, D&W Originals Cheddar, D&W Originals Herbed Turkey, and lettuce into 2 inch squares
Cut slices of cooked bacon into thirds
On a 10- to 12-inch skewer, layer bread, lettuce, cheese, bacon and cherry tomato
Repeat once more, then top with last piece of bread
Serve with a side of D&W Hoagie Dressing for dipping
